Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:26.65,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,We were just passing by, \NWhen suddenly we met {めぐりあい　すれちがう}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:35.47,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Just like headlights of this familiar city \NThat come and go {この都会(まち)を行き交う　Headlight}
