Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:21.50,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Even if we had to part once, \NWe'll meet again somewhere {何処かで逢えると　別れたけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:26.02,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,I came to realize -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.13,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Until the end of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:39.83,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Friends or lovers once \NCan't return to being them again {友達にも　恋人にも　戻れない事だけ　分かっていた}
